pmmd.notes:
APG3 adds 6 families to the order: placement of 5 of them (Didiereaceae, Anacampserotaceae, 
Talinaceae, Lophiocarpaceae and Limeaceae) is based on topology in Stevens' APweb;
Gisekiaceae is unplaced on APweb, but Cuenoud et al. 2002 (AmJBot 89:132-144) suggest its placement in the Sarcobataceae polytomy;
